snippet.title: Magicraft V1.0 OUT NOW! Billions Builds Blow up Magicraft
snippet.description:
Dear great Magicians, the 1.0 version of Magicraft is now available, priced at $52, with a two-week 20% discount!
There is endless abyss and monsters that never stop attacking ........
You never know what's waiting for you, let alone the horrors of the Old Gods that await you at the end of journey.
Luckily, spells, wands, and relics are your most reliable companions.
Make good use of them, they will bring you billions of  surprises ...... (or is it scares?)

Steam：https://store.steampowered.com/app/2103140
Discord：https://discord.com/invite/magicraft-1029926808516309093
